casebody.data:
No. 54,

Orig.

United States v. Florida et al. [For earlier orders herein, see, e. g., 423 U. S. 1011.]

Report of Special Master on motion of defendants for leave to file counterclaim received and ordered filed. Exceptions, if any, with supporting briefs to Report may be filed by the parties within 45 days. Reply briefs, if any, to such exceptions may be filed within 30 days.
